Sinesis and Sinister stepped back. Dracona's programming kicked in and she
stared at Scorponok.

"Where am I?" Dracona asked.

"Uh, your in the Predacon base." Sinesis said.

"Oh, yeah, but I remember, I was a Maximal." Dracona said. Sinesis and
Sinister gasp, their device didn't take care of her memory.

"I'm a Predacon." Dracona said surprised.

Sinesis and Sinister nod.

"I feel good." Dracona said. She smiled and the scar on her eye glows.
Dracona looks at Sinesis and Sinister.

"I'm Sinister, this is my bone head brother Sinesis!" Sinister said. Sinesis
grabs Sinister by the throat and starts to choke him. Dracona turns to
Scorponok.

"Who are you?" Dracona asked Scorponok...
